<%# Status mark plus its word. Shape carries the meaning — filled / open /
    barred — so it survives greyscale and every form of colour blindness;
    hue only reinforces. The word is mandatory: never render the mark alone.
    Green never appears here. "Settled" is a judgement, not an issuance. %>
<span class="state st-<%= state %>">
  <%= render "shared/state_mark", state: state %>
  <%= label %>
</span>
